# 🛍️ Diwali Sales Analysis

## 📌 Objective
To analyze sales data during the Diwali season to uncover patterns in customer demographics and buying behavior, helping businesses plan marketing campaigns effectively.

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Python
- Jupyter Notebook
- Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn

## 📊 Key Tasks Performed
- Cleaned and handled missing values
- Created demographic segments (age, gender, marital status)
- Visualized purchase behavior across product categories
- Identified top-selling products and high-value customers

## 📌 Insights
- Married women in the age group of 26–35 were the most frequent buyers.
- Electronics and clothing were the top-selling categories.

## 🧑‍💻 About Me
This project allowed me to explore customer segmentation and apply EDA techniques to festive sales data using Python.
